flowchart TD
    Sources[Data Sources\nDatabases, streams, APIs, files] --> Ingest[Ingestion Layer\nBatch loaders and stream connectors]
    Ingest --> RawZone[Raw Zone\nNative format, append-only\nJSON, CSV, Avro, logs]
    RawZone --> Transform1[Transformation Job\nSpark, dbt, Glue]
    Transform1 --> CuratedZone[Curated Zone\nCleaned, validated, conformed\nParquet, partitioned by date]
    CuratedZone --> Transform2[Aggregation Job\nPurpose-built models]
    Transform2 --> ServingZone[Serving Zone\nDomain aggregates\nML features, finance rollups]
    ServingZone --> Warehouse[Data Warehouse\nSQL analytics engine]
    ServingZone --> MLPlatform[ML Platform\nFeature store, training data]
    ServingZone --> BI[BI Tools and Dashboards]
    RawZone --> Catalog[Data Catalog\nLineage, ownership, access policies]
    CuratedZone --> Catalog
    ServingZone --> Catalog
